label: uncl7233
comment: Code specifying information related to packaging.

values.label: Product ingredients not marked on package
values.comment: The ingredients of the product are not marked on the packaging of the product.

values.label: Product price not marked on packaging
values.comment: The product price is not marked on the packaging of the product.

values.label: Product best before date not marked on product package
values.comment: The product best before date is not marked on the packaging of the product.

values.label: Package not marked recyclable
values.comment: Package is not marked as recyclable.

values.label: Promotional details marked
values.comment: A code indicating that promotional details have been marked on the package.

values.label: Labeled according to general EAN.UCC specifications for clothing and fashion accessories
values.comment: The item is labeled according to the general EAN.UCC specifications for clothing and fashion accessories.

values.label: Sell-by date marked on package
values.comment: The package is marked with the last date on which the item may be sold.

values.label: Use-by date marked on package
values.comment: The package is marked with the last date on which the item may be used.

values.label: Packaging / manufacturing date marked on package
values.comment: The package is marked with the date of the packaging or manufacturing of the item.

values.label: No freshness date marked on package
values.comment: Package is not marked with any kind of date indicating freshness, such as use-by, best before or packaging date.

values.label: Package best before date marked
values.comment: Package is marked with the product best before date.

values.label: Package marked recyclable
values.comment: The package is marked recyclable.

values.label: Package marked returnable
values.comment: The package is marked returnable.

values.label: Product marking
values.comment: The information is related to product marking.

values.label: Type of package
values.comment: The information is related to the type of package.

values.label: Package specifications
values.comment: The information specifies the package.

values.label: Package protection
values.comment: The information is related to protection of the package.

values.label: Tarping
values.comment: The information describes how coverage with tarpaulins is to be provided.

values.label: Platform/skid location
values.comment: The information describes the platform or skid location.

values.label: Bearing piece location
values.comment: The information gives the location of the load bearing piece.

values.label: Skid/pallet type
values.comment: The information describes the type of skid or pallet.

values.label: Placement on carrier
values.comment: The information describes the placement on the carrier.

values.label: Spacing directions
values.comment: Descriptions to be provided.

values.label: Unloading device
values.comment: The information specifies the unloading device which must be used to handle the package.

values.label: Unloading equipment
values.comment: The information specifies the unloading equipment which must be used to handle the package.

values.label: Packing method
values.comment: The method used in packing the commodity, e.g. hermetically sealed, repacked in original container.

values.label: Packing group I
values.comment: Substances presenting high danger.

values.label: Packing group II
values.comment: Substances presenting medium danger.

values.label: Packing group III
values.comment: Substances presenting low danger.

values.label: Package barcoded EAN-13 or EAN-8
values.comment: The package is barcoded with EAN-13 or EAN-8 code.

values.label: Package barcoded ITF-14 or ITF-6
values.comment: The package is barcoded with ITF-14 or ITF-6 code.

values.label: Package barcoded UCC or EAN-128
values.comment: The package is barcoded with UCC or EAN-128 code.

values.label: Package price marked
values.comment: The package is marked with the price.

values.label: Product ingredients marked on package
values.comment: The ingredients of the product contained in a package are marked on that package.

values.label: Core characteristics
values.comment: Specifies the characteristics of the core of the package.

values.label: Shipping requirement
values.comment: The packaging as per shipping requirement.

values.label: Customs requirement
values.comment: The packaging as per Customs requirement.

values.label: Transport contract requirement
values.comment: The packaging as per transport contract requirement.

values.label: Preservation method
values.comment: The packaging related information is for methods of preservation.

values.label: Product marking pattern
values.comment: The information describes the pattern used to mark the product.

values.label: Product marking location
values.comment: The information provides the location of the product marking.

values.label: Package/container mark location
values.comment: The information provides the location of a package or container mark.

values.label: Marking method
values.comment: The information details the marking method.

values.label: Package never EPC tagged
values.comment: The package will never be tagged with an EPC (Electronic Product Code) transponder.

values.label: Package sometimes EPC tagged
values.comment: The package will sometimes be tagged with an EPC (Electronic Product Code) transponder.

values.label: Receiving facility limitations
values.comment: The information describes limitations which apply to a receiving facility.

values.label: Tagging/bar code instructions
values.comment: The information provides instructions as to how a package is to be tagged or have a bar code applied to it.

values.label: Shipping package labelling
values.comment: The labelling of a package in which goods are shipped.

values.label: Shipping package sealing
values.comment: The sealing particulars of a package in which goods are shipped.

values.label: Optional packaging procedure
values.comment: To indicate an optional procedure for packaging.

values.label: Cleaning or drying specification
values.comment: Identification of the cleaning or drying specification.

values.label: Cushioning thickness specification
values.comment: Identification of the cushioning thickness specification.

values.label: Cushioning and dunnage specification
values.comment: Identification of the cushioning and dunnage specification.

values.label: Level of preservation specification
values.comment: Identification of the level of preservation specification.

values.label: Preservation material specification
values.comment: Identification of the preservation material specification.

values.label: Unit container specification
values.comment: Identification of the unit container specification.

values.label: Material wrapping specification
values.comment: Identification of the material wrapping specification.

values.label: Package bar-coded and EPC tagged
values.comment: The package is bar-coded and tagged with an EPC (Electronic Product Code) transponder.

values.label: Package EPC tagged only
values.comment: The package is tagged with an EPC (Electronic Product Code) transponder only.

values.label: Marked with display until date
values.comment: Package is marked with the date by which the product should be removed from the display location.

values.label: Package marked with a variable measure barcode
values.comment: The package is marked with a variable measure barcode.

values.label: Package marked with fixed measure barcode.
values.comment: The package is marked with a fixed measure barcode.

values.label: RFID not on packaging
values.comment: To indicate that the packaging of the trade item is not tagged with a Radio Frequency ID.

values.label: RFID on packaging
values.comment: To indicate that the packaging of the trade item is tagged with a Radio Frequency ID.

values.label: Package not marked returnable
values.comment: The package is not marked returnable.

values.label: Gift wrapping
values.comment: Trade item is packaged in a gift wrapping.

values.label: Accompanied by greeting card
values.comment: Trade item is accompanied by a greeting card.
